This form should contain all components that are allowed to be used on a phone (mobile-enabled).
Open this User Input task and check the 'Enable support for mobile clients and additional web browsers (some components will not be available)' option.
Click on 'Validate', 'Save', 'Save and close' and you should not see any error messages.

This form should contain all NOT mobile-enabled components or configurations.
Open this User Input task and check the 'Enable support for mobile clients and additional web browsers (some components will not be available)' option.
